Volcanic Stove is a The Lion King themed piece of [[:Category:Cooking Stations|cooking station]] furniture.

It functions as a [[:Category:Cooking Stations|cooking station]], and once placed it can be interacted with to make [[Cooking|meal recipes]].

Once it is placed in the world, the Player can '''Interact''' with the object to toggle the fire on and off.


